WEBVTT

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.920
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:14.640
Guard!

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:50.080
Your new cellmate.

00:00:56.800 --> 00:00:57.840
What are you in for?

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:17.480
2 DAYS EARLIER

00:01:27.440 --> 00:01:28.280
You kidding?

00:01:28.360 --> 00:01:30.640
I wouldn't have called otherwise.

00:01:32.040 --> 00:01:33.600
Impossible. Check again.

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:35.240
I checked it all night!

00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:38.760
Original clasp.

00:01:38.840 --> 00:01:41.520
Original setting.
No marks on the gemstones.

00:01:41.600 --> 00:01:44.600
I guarantee you
this necklace has never been taken apart.

00:01:45.160 --> 00:01:46.120
If so,

00:01:46.200 --> 00:01:49.200
the story about the scattered gemstones
is bullshit.

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:51.960
The necklace never left
the Pellegrinis' safe?

00:01:52.440 --> 00:01:54.160
-Why would they lie?
-No idea.

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:56.480
Maybe they lied about everything else,

00:01:56.560 --> 00:01:58.880
including my father's theft.

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:01.640
For 25 years,
I've believed my dad to be a thief.

00:02:02.720 --> 00:02:05.800
-I've been wrong for 25 years.
-Easy, Assane.

00:02:06.480 --> 00:02:08.280
You have the necklace. You made it out.

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:10.880
-Who cares about the rest?
-Who cares about truth?

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:12.920
No, I'm not saying that, but…

00:02:15.040 --> 00:02:16.960
You told me
you'd stop after this necklace,

00:02:17.440 --> 00:02:19.120
that Raoul needed his dad.

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:22.240
-Think of him.
-That's all I'm doing.

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:25.520
He should know who his grandpa was.

00:02:27.760 --> 00:02:28.720
Take them out.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:32.120
-Assane.
-I know what I'm doing.

00:02:34.640 --> 00:02:35.960
What are you doing?

00:02:37.720 --> 00:02:38.800
Nothing special.

00:02:43.880 --> 00:02:45.320
-Hiding something?
-Me?

00:02:48.440 --> 00:02:49.400
Not at all.

00:02:50.200 --> 00:02:52.440
-He doesn't believe me!
-Kids…

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:08.440
Police! Open up!

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:14.680
Lt. Dumont! Open up!

00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:26.080
Don't make me break it down.

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:32.080
Sit down.

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:43.520
-How old are you?
-Sixteen.

00:03:45.360 --> 00:03:47.680
-You live alone?
-I live with my mother.

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:50.760
-She'll be back.
-Really?

00:03:58.120 --> 00:03:59.240
Let's wait for her.

00:04:11.240 --> 00:04:13.520
Pack your things.
We're going to Social Services.

00:04:17.640 --> 00:04:18.640
Did you hear?

00:04:19.840 --> 00:04:21.800
Come on! Hurry up!

00:05:08.080 --> 00:05:09.320
What's the holdup?

00:05:37.320 --> 00:05:39.680
Work on your escape technique, sonny!

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:52.920
-Hi, Mom.
-Hi.

00:05:53.440 --> 00:05:56.280
Just passing through.
I'm off to the foundation.

00:05:56.360 --> 00:05:58.320
I heard about your father's necklace.

00:05:59.080 --> 00:06:00.400
They recovered a copy.

00:06:01.440 --> 00:06:03.040
Probably driving him crazy.

00:06:03.520 --> 00:06:05.480
You seem heartbroken about it.

00:06:07.520 --> 00:06:09.640
Don't worry. The police have a lead.

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:12.280
Says the media,
but since he owns most of it,

00:06:12.360 --> 00:06:13.400
I have my doubts.

00:06:14.480 --> 00:06:17.560
The necklace vanished again
after 25 years. Bad luck.

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:19.560
Back luck, indeed.

00:06:19.640 --> 00:06:22.360
It really upset him at the time.

00:06:22.440 --> 00:06:24.040
It could be even worse now.

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:26.160
How are you?

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:28.480
Slowly but surely fading away

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:30.960
in this gilded cage your father gave me.

00:06:31.480 --> 00:06:33.600
He did pick out the orchids.

00:06:34.400 --> 00:06:36.880
-Steered clear of chrysanthemums.
-Stop it.

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:39.960
-He doesn't hate you.
-No, he's afraid of me.

00:06:40.040 --> 00:06:41.800
I know where the bodies are.

00:06:42.520 --> 00:06:43.880
Watch out for yourself.

00:06:44.440 --> 00:06:46.560
He adores you, you adore him, but…

00:06:46.640 --> 00:06:47.760
he says it himself,

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:50.520
you're with him or against him.

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:53.400
Goodbye, Mom.

00:06:54.200 --> 00:06:55.280
Goodbye, Juliette.

00:07:01.720 --> 00:07:02.800
Goodbye, François.

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:04.280
Ms. Pellegrini?

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:06.160
For you.

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:07.720
-Thank you.
-My pleasure.

00:07:10.720 --> 00:07:15.400
LUXEMBOURG GARDENS, 14:00
NO POLICE

00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:29.680
-Bye.
-Bye. Thank you.

00:07:35.800 --> 00:07:37.800
Medium rare, no onions.

00:07:37.880 --> 00:07:39.160
There. Thank you.

00:07:39.880 --> 00:07:41.360
Yes, madam? That's right.

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:42.960
Medium rare, no onions.

00:07:43.040 --> 00:07:44.040
Thank you.

00:08:20.240 --> 00:08:22.000
You're in a hurry. Good, so am I.

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:24.320
How much do you want?

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:26.600
My price is zero.

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:28.360
I don't want money.

00:08:31.120 --> 00:08:32.160
I want answers.

00:08:33.640 --> 00:08:35.680
I can't see his face. I can't hear!

00:08:35.760 --> 00:08:36.920
His hand is over the mic.

00:08:37.000 --> 00:08:38.680
Fix it, goddamn it!

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:40.720
Fix it! I want to hear them!

00:08:40.800 --> 00:08:43.840
All units, the Louvre thief is there!

00:08:43.920 --> 00:08:46.720
Don't intervene until he makes a move.
Got it?

00:08:46.800 --> 00:08:48.440
I said no police, Juliette.

00:08:49.240 --> 00:08:52.520
-You stole the necklace from us?
-I'm asking the questions.

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:54.280
Why did you lie?

00:08:55.040 --> 00:08:57.040
-Lie? About what?
-The necklace.

00:08:58.360 --> 00:08:59.400
It wasn't taken apart.

00:09:00.400 --> 00:09:02.040
That means my father never stole it.

00:09:03.920 --> 00:09:05.040
That's true.

00:09:06.120 --> 00:09:07.960
I mean, it wasn't taken apart.

00:09:09.240 --> 00:09:12.840
My father and I got this idea
of the scattered gemstones

00:09:12.920 --> 00:09:15.120
to build up the buzz before the sale.

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:19.200
Daddy bought it back
from a jeweler in South Africa.

00:09:20.640 --> 00:09:22.760
-That doesn't hold up.
-I swear.

00:09:22.840 --> 00:09:25.160
-Look at me. You know me.
-Stop it.

00:09:25.240 --> 00:09:27.840
Shit, they know each other. Look at that.

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:31.720
I'm sure they do!
Pellegrini is playing us.

00:09:31.800 --> 00:09:34.200
Belkacem, I want to hear! Get closer!

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:37.000
Get between them and the exit.

00:09:37.080 --> 00:09:40.000
If my father finds out, you're a dead man.

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:43.280
Give me back the necklace.
I'll tell the cops I don't know you.

00:09:43.360 --> 00:09:45.080
Tell me my father was innocent.

00:09:45.160 --> 00:09:46.960
I would love to tell you that,

00:09:47.040 --> 00:09:49.080
but he was guilty and signed a confession.

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:54.360
I think you don't know your father.

00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:07.480
OK! He's on the move! All units!

00:10:07.560 --> 00:10:09.120
Bring him in!

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:11.200
Stop!

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:13.400
Stop!

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:14.560
Get him!

00:10:14.640 --> 00:10:16.800
He left on a bike. Get him!

00:10:27.680 --> 00:10:30.120
-We can't let him get away!
-We're on him.

00:10:30.200 --> 00:10:31.640
Gotta get him this time!

00:10:37.240 --> 00:10:38.840
He's headed for Vavin.

00:10:38.920 --> 00:10:40.080
Catch him at the exit.

00:10:43.000 --> 00:10:44.280
What's this?

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:53.600
How did he manage that?

00:10:53.680 --> 00:10:55.000
Guys, headed for the Senate!

00:10:56.560 --> 00:10:58.040
I can't believe it! Shit!

00:10:59.040 --> 00:11:00.920
He's headed for the observatory.

00:11:01.400 --> 00:11:03.960
Exit six, let's go! Everyone go!

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:10.880
Stop!

00:11:11.920 --> 00:11:14.040
-On the ground!
-Come here, dammit!

00:11:14.120 --> 00:11:17.040
-Give me everything!
-Your hands.

00:11:17.120 --> 00:11:18.080
It's not him.

00:11:18.640 --> 00:11:20.680
Burger, medium rare, no onions?

00:11:20.760 --> 00:11:23.160
-It's not him!
-Don't move!

00:11:25.320 --> 00:11:27.360
Shit, dammit!

00:11:27.440 --> 00:11:28.800
Take off your mask!

00:11:29.800 --> 00:11:32.000
-Show your face.
-Lock the park.

00:11:32.080 --> 00:11:33.360
No one gets out, OK?

00:11:34.560 --> 00:11:36.280
It's impossible! Where is he?

00:11:36.760 --> 00:11:37.600
Shit!

00:12:26.200 --> 00:12:30.240
FOR ASSANE

00:12:33.720 --> 00:12:35.600
My son, I am ashamed.

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:38.280
I am guilty of what I am accused of.

00:12:38.840 --> 00:12:40.920
I wanted to give you a better life.

00:12:41.000 --> 00:12:42.000
I failed.

00:12:42.640 --> 00:12:44.880
So I hope you will forgive me.

00:12:45.600 --> 00:12:46.880
Remember,

00:12:46.960 --> 00:12:50.040
the truth will always lie in "libraryes."

00:12:50.680 --> 00:12:52.800
Don't "comet" the same mistakes I did.

00:12:53.400 --> 00:12:54.400
I love you.

00:12:55.400 --> 00:12:56.240
Dad.

00:12:57.600 --> 00:13:00.040
De Gaulle with one L?

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:03.200
Be careful, Assane.
Spelling is everything.

00:13:03.280 --> 00:13:05.200
If your mother could see you!

00:13:28.800 --> 00:13:31.360
MINISTRY OF INTERNAL AFFAIRS

00:13:31.440 --> 00:13:33.880
KILLED HIMSELF IN HIS CELL

00:13:47.000 --> 00:13:50.040
-I always make spelling mistakes.
-You and I both.

00:13:50.640 --> 00:13:53.480
My father, never. Let alone two in a row.

00:13:53.560 --> 00:13:55.920
-Yeah? So?
-Look.

00:13:57.520 --> 00:13:59.560
-"Comet," "libraryes."
-Yes.

00:13:59.640 --> 00:14:01.160
-And?
-I looked around.

00:14:02.160 --> 00:14:05.640
There was a guy in prison with my dad.
Called Étienne Comet.

00:14:06.200 --> 00:14:07.320
C-O-M-E-T.

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:09.560
Where did he work?

00:14:10.920 --> 00:14:12.800
-The library.
-Exactly.

00:14:13.840 --> 00:14:15.000
Hang on, Assane…

00:14:15.640 --> 00:14:17.760
That's called a coincidence.

00:14:19.200 --> 00:14:22.400
-Seriously?
-A hidden message in spelling mistakes?

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:25.280
-You're reaching.
-You don't understand.

00:14:27.960 --> 00:14:31.960
It's been under my nose for years.
Trying to prove his innocence.

00:14:32.560 --> 00:14:33.640
Thanks to this Comet.

00:14:34.120 --> 00:14:35.200
And I did nothing.

00:14:40.240 --> 00:14:41.120
You're right.

00:14:42.280 --> 00:14:45.240
You have doubts.
See this to the end. Go see Comet.

00:14:45.800 --> 00:14:47.640
-Where is he?
-In prison.

00:14:48.160 --> 00:14:51.080
-Make a visit request.
-He's sick. He doesn't leave his cell.

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:54.400
-Well…
-I'll find another way.

00:14:57.680 --> 00:14:58.760
-No!
-Yes.

00:14:58.840 --> 00:15:01.800
-No!
-You said, "See this to the end."

00:15:03.160 --> 00:15:04.160
I must see Comet.

00:15:05.640 --> 00:15:08.280
Fucking hell! Shit! Assane!

00:15:08.840 --> 00:15:09.680
Wait!

00:15:10.400 --> 00:15:11.240
Wait!

00:15:14.040 --> 00:15:14.880
Wait!

00:15:31.600 --> 00:15:32.920
Visitor. Djibril Traoré.

00:15:38.400 --> 00:15:39.320
Hey, Cousin.

00:15:42.040 --> 00:15:43.040
Have a seat.

00:15:44.280 --> 00:15:46.080
You and I are cousins?

00:15:47.720 --> 00:15:48.920
I don't have any.

00:15:50.120 --> 00:15:51.480
Well, now you have one.

00:15:52.360 --> 00:15:54.360
Your cousin has a present for you.

00:15:57.480 --> 00:15:59.240
You… get out.

00:16:00.520 --> 00:16:01.680
I go inside instead.

00:16:09.360 --> 00:16:10.360
Hang on.

00:16:10.840 --> 00:16:12.400
Are you totally stupid?

00:16:13.200 --> 00:16:15.560
Oh, I know! Actually…

00:16:15.640 --> 00:16:18.080
The guards won't notice anything

00:16:18.160 --> 00:16:22.360
because you and I totally look like twins.

00:16:29.320 --> 00:16:30.160
There.

00:16:32.880 --> 00:16:34.360
The guards just switched.

00:16:39.200 --> 00:16:40.720
And the other inmates?

00:16:40.800 --> 00:16:42.920
You've been quarantined for a week.

00:16:43.880 --> 00:16:46.480
Tonight, you're being moved to a cell.

00:16:47.680 --> 00:16:49.280
Nobody knows you in prison.

00:16:50.200 --> 00:16:52.680
OK, but aren't you forgetting something?

00:16:56.400 --> 00:16:58.520
Shit, the handcuffs.

00:16:58.600 --> 00:17:00.600
Shit, the handcuffs.

00:17:01.120 --> 00:17:02.240
I'm so stupid.

00:17:04.360 --> 00:17:06.040
How did I not think of that?

00:17:12.320 --> 00:17:14.840
-Know the handcuff trick?
-The what?

00:17:16.520 --> 00:17:17.720
Now you know it.

00:17:19.520 --> 00:17:21.200
Guard! We're done.

00:17:22.480 --> 00:17:26.560
I know why you're here.
Deal so much as a joint, I'll find you.

00:17:28.160 --> 00:17:30.120
I got you out. I can get you back in.

00:17:34.080 --> 00:17:36.040
-See you, Cousin.
-Go ahead.

00:17:38.440 --> 00:17:39.280
Guard.

00:17:51.160 --> 00:17:52.440
Give Auntie a kiss for me!

00:17:52.520 --> 00:17:53.360
Guard.

00:18:36.760 --> 00:18:38.880
I know it's hard here at first.

00:18:40.120 --> 00:18:41.440
You'll get used to it.

00:18:42.520 --> 00:18:44.520
We respect all individual faiths here.

00:18:46.880 --> 00:18:49.400
Personally,
one book often brought me…

00:18:50.160 --> 00:18:51.520
answers…

00:18:52.840 --> 00:18:53.840
and comfort.

00:18:59.480 --> 00:19:00.520
Welcome, my boy.

00:19:03.440 --> 00:19:05.480
THE HOLY BIBLE

00:19:09.880 --> 00:19:12.920
Ms. Pellegrini, one thing is bothering me.

00:19:14.080 --> 00:19:17.680
Based on the video, you and the suspect…

00:19:19.240 --> 00:19:20.560
seemed to know each other.

00:19:22.280 --> 00:19:26.120
Lieutenant, it sounds like
you're treating me as a suspect.

00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:29.760
-Am I accused of anything?
-No, not at all.

00:19:30.320 --> 00:19:31.720
If that's the case, no problem.

00:19:32.200 --> 00:19:34.600
You can detain me.
I'll send for my lawyers.

00:19:34.680 --> 00:19:36.880
You'll get fired within 15 minutes. OK?

00:19:37.640 --> 00:19:39.560
-No. hang on--
-Change your tone.

00:19:40.840 --> 00:19:42.760
And focus on your investigation.

00:19:43.440 --> 00:19:46.760
I'm asking you
what you two said to each other. OK?

00:19:47.840 --> 00:19:48.680
Absolutely.

00:19:51.240 --> 00:19:52.360
I told him that…

00:19:53.680 --> 00:19:56.080
the officer in charge is a moron

00:19:56.720 --> 00:19:58.520
who got me a plastic necklace.

00:20:01.240 --> 00:20:02.240
No more notes?

00:20:05.720 --> 00:20:07.320
Find our necklace, Captain.

00:20:09.640 --> 00:20:12.280
You don't want to disappoint
your superiors, do you?

00:20:13.360 --> 00:20:15.080
-No, madam.
-Very good.

00:20:18.600 --> 00:20:19.440
Thank you.

00:20:33.960 --> 00:20:35.480
I made coffee if you'd like some.

00:20:36.120 --> 00:20:37.120
Thanks a lot.

00:21:21.920 --> 00:21:22.760
Hey.

00:21:24.760 --> 00:21:26.360
Know a guy named Comet?

00:21:27.520 --> 00:21:28.480
Étienne Comet.

00:21:30.080 --> 00:21:31.800
-What do you want with him?
-Nothing.

00:21:31.880 --> 00:21:33.280
Just a mutual friend.

00:21:34.400 --> 00:21:35.520
Who is your friend?

00:21:39.560 --> 00:21:41.920
I'm quitting. Not good for breathing.

00:21:43.840 --> 00:21:44.800
You interested?

00:21:50.320 --> 00:21:51.520
Cell 241.

00:21:56.120 --> 00:21:57.920
I want to know everything about him.

00:22:29.320 --> 00:22:31.800
Vincent Morville, tell me about the theft.

00:22:36.240 --> 00:22:39.080
His name was Luis Perenna.
Never seen him before.

00:22:50.560 --> 00:22:52.800
-241, Comet. Leroy.
-Yeah.

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:56.080
-Guard?
-Yes, coming.

00:22:57.160 --> 00:22:59.240
-Where's Étienne?
-At the infirmary.

00:22:59.720 --> 00:23:02.680
-When is he back?
-I don't think he's coming back.

00:23:03.320 --> 00:23:04.320
OK, thank you.

00:23:17.680 --> 00:23:19.080
Hey, who are you?

00:23:20.560 --> 00:23:23.360
-Who are you?
-Djibril. Djibril Traoré.

00:23:25.720 --> 00:23:27.440
He owes me 1,000 euros worth of dope.

00:23:27.520 --> 00:23:30.160
-Now you owe me. You've got three days.
-Three?

00:23:30.240 --> 00:23:32.000
Is it too much time, Djibril?

00:23:34.520 --> 00:23:35.360
No, it's fine.

00:23:35.840 --> 00:23:36.920
-Yeah.
-It's fine.

00:23:38.440 --> 00:23:40.720
-What's going on here?
-Nothing.

00:23:56.280 --> 00:23:59.760
-He just got here. Already sick.
-It's all right. I'll take care of it.

00:24:05.040 --> 00:24:06.120
Have a seat.

00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:13.440
So, what's the matter?

00:24:14.600 --> 00:24:16.560
It started with pain all over.

00:24:17.680 --> 00:24:19.040
Thought I was pregnant.

00:24:20.000 --> 00:24:21.240
But that's not it.

00:24:22.040 --> 00:24:23.360
Probably not!

00:24:23.440 --> 00:24:24.840
I figured…

00:24:25.680 --> 00:24:28.160
a night in the infirmary. For observation.

00:24:28.920 --> 00:24:30.160
It'd be wiser, right?

00:24:32.400 --> 00:24:33.240
Listen…

00:24:34.040 --> 00:24:35.240
I know it's hard at first.

00:24:36.520 --> 00:24:39.040
But a big boy like you
will get used to it. Right?

00:24:42.200 --> 00:24:43.200
And my night here?

00:24:44.400 --> 00:24:45.840
You'll have to do better.

00:24:45.920 --> 00:24:47.360
-Oh yeah?
-Yeah.

00:24:51.200 --> 00:24:52.040
Got a minute?

00:24:52.120 --> 00:24:54.360
-No, I'm going to see the boss.
-Please, a minute.

00:24:54.440 --> 00:24:56.400
I need to show you something incredible.

00:25:00.480 --> 00:25:01.440
Look.

00:25:03.320 --> 00:25:04.160
Paul Sernine.

00:25:04.880 --> 00:25:05.720
Luis Perenna.

00:25:07.640 --> 00:25:10.320
-What are you doing?
-Don't you see?

00:25:12.640 --> 00:25:13.960
They are both anagrams.

00:25:16.840 --> 00:25:18.320
-And?
-It makes sense.

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:21.080
A link between the thief
and Arsène Lupin.

00:25:21.160 --> 00:25:24.000
We should study this.
Do I talk to Laugier?

00:25:25.280 --> 00:25:26.920
Yeah, sure. Great idea.

00:25:27.560 --> 00:25:30.800
If you want to look like an idiot.
He's in a good mood.

00:25:30.880 --> 00:25:32.520
Seriously, what's this?

00:25:32.600 --> 00:25:34.800
What's next? D'Artagnan?
Three Little Pigs?

00:25:34.880 --> 00:25:36.920
Get back to work. Let's make progress.

00:25:38.080 --> 00:25:40.680
Can't we do better than this?

00:25:41.160 --> 00:25:44.160
We're the police. The guy puts on
a costume, and we're done!

00:25:44.720 --> 00:25:46.880
What's this mess? He is playing us!

00:25:47.400 --> 00:25:49.560
We're nowhere. We suck!

00:25:49.640 --> 00:25:51.440
The investigation is bullshit!

00:26:06.520 --> 00:26:08.120
-Tell me.
-What do you want?

00:26:09.680 --> 00:26:13.040
-How were you getting the dope?
-Why the hell do you care?

00:26:13.640 --> 00:26:15.040
Just curious.

00:26:15.120 --> 00:26:16.920
You stupid? He swallowed it.

00:26:17.000 --> 00:26:19.720
-Then out of his ass.
-There you go.

00:26:20.280 --> 00:26:22.640
That's where you're gonna put your cash.

00:26:24.240 --> 00:26:25.520
Does he have a death wish?

00:26:39.640 --> 00:26:40.640
There you go.

00:26:42.760 --> 00:26:45.000
I suppose you did this to yourself?

00:26:45.080 --> 00:26:47.800
Right. A stupid accident.
I was shaving, and…

00:26:48.520 --> 00:26:49.520
I slipped.

00:26:58.240 --> 00:27:00.560
All right. I'll keep you in overnight.

00:27:02.000 --> 00:27:02.840
Finally!

00:27:04.520 --> 00:27:06.800
Make some friends.
It's useful in here.

00:27:12.120 --> 00:27:12.960
Good night.

00:27:30.480 --> 00:27:31.320
Étienne?

00:27:33.960 --> 00:27:34.800
Étienne?

00:27:36.720 --> 00:27:37.560
Étienne.

00:27:38.680 --> 00:27:40.040
My name is Assane Diop.

00:27:41.960 --> 00:27:43.920
My father was named Babakar Diop.

00:27:45.520 --> 00:27:46.800
You were in prison together.

00:27:54.360 --> 00:27:55.400
Étienne?

00:27:56.840 --> 00:27:58.480
-Babakar.
-Yeah!

00:27:59.160 --> 00:28:00.160
Do you remember?

00:28:01.760 --> 00:28:02.880
Yeah, maybe, yeah.

00:28:05.520 --> 00:28:08.560
-He stole a necklace, right?
-Yes. Well, no.

00:28:09.920 --> 00:28:11.360
That's why I'm here.

00:28:11.440 --> 00:28:12.920
He was wrongly convicted.

00:28:15.760 --> 00:28:17.240
I don't know your father.

00:28:20.000 --> 00:28:20.840
No.

00:28:21.840 --> 00:28:23.640
-That's impossible.
-Yes.

00:28:25.000 --> 00:28:26.080
What do you mean?

00:28:26.600 --> 00:28:28.200
He was alone in his cell.

00:28:29.280 --> 00:28:30.600
Always under surveillance.

00:28:32.480 --> 00:28:34.320
I only saw him once, because…

00:28:35.160 --> 00:28:36.880
I brought him a book…

00:28:37.720 --> 00:28:39.720
when I was working at the library.

00:28:40.560 --> 00:28:41.400
That's all.

00:28:43.360 --> 00:28:44.960
There has to be something else.

00:28:46.120 --> 00:28:47.120
Please, try.

00:28:47.920 --> 00:28:48.760
Étienne.

00:28:52.000 --> 00:28:53.760
When he returned the book, he said…

00:28:53.840 --> 00:28:54.720
Yeah?

00:28:55.520 --> 00:28:58.040
…that if someone came
on his behalf someday,

00:29:00.080 --> 00:29:01.480
he wanted me to give it to him.

00:29:03.920 --> 00:29:06.040
He said all the answers were inside.

00:29:07.560 --> 00:29:09.040
You still have this book?

00:29:11.400 --> 00:29:12.360
Maybe, yeah.

00:29:13.440 --> 00:29:14.760
Look through my stuff.

00:29:44.880 --> 00:29:46.040
You're not playing?

00:29:51.920 --> 00:29:54.080
Came this morning. From your father.

00:29:55.360 --> 00:29:57.280
The guards found it in his cell.

00:30:10.280 --> 00:30:12.560
Have you heard of the Andrésy school?

00:30:13.560 --> 00:30:15.840
One of the best private schools in France.

00:30:16.760 --> 00:30:19.200
Someone wants you to attend next year.

00:30:22.120 --> 00:30:24.160
A generous donor has paid for everything.

00:30:27.440 --> 00:30:28.280
Assane.

00:30:29.240 --> 00:30:31.040
You'll get a real education there.

00:30:31.800 --> 00:30:33.160
You'll become somebody.

00:30:36.000 --> 00:30:39.200
This is your chance. Seize it.
Nothing is written in stone.

00:30:41.120 --> 00:30:42.360
I'm glad you like it.

00:30:57.200 --> 00:30:59.200
My son, I am ashamed.

00:30:59.800 --> 00:31:01.520
I am guilty of what I am accused of.

00:31:02.440 --> 00:31:05.640
I wanted to give you a better life.
I failed.

00:31:18.040 --> 00:31:19.280
-241?
-Yes.

00:31:23.240 --> 00:31:25.200
Shit, clean sheets. It's the Ritz!

00:31:25.280 --> 00:31:27.200
-Where are Étienne's things?
-Second shelf.

00:31:49.360 --> 00:31:50.520
Good luck.

00:32:01.120 --> 00:32:03.720
THE EXPLOITS OF ARSÈNE LUPIN

00:32:05.000 --> 00:32:06.320
How was science class?

00:32:10.320 --> 00:32:11.640
Raoul, I'm talking to you.

00:32:12.800 --> 00:32:14.520
Your science test, did it go OK?

00:32:19.400 --> 00:32:20.880
Is that the book Dad gave you?

00:32:25.320 --> 00:32:26.920
He scribbled on every page.

00:32:30.320 --> 00:32:32.240
You prefer reading to video games now?

00:32:36.440 --> 00:32:37.440
How about that?

00:32:51.160 --> 00:32:52.080
"Am…"

00:32:57.760 --> 00:32:58.880
"Innocent…"

00:33:07.360 --> 00:33:09.040
TRAP

00:33:46.560 --> 00:33:48.120
"I am innocent,

00:33:48.200 --> 00:33:49.960
trapped by Anne…

00:33:51.080 --> 00:33:52.000
Pellegrini."

00:34:19.880 --> 00:34:21.400
Bogdan hopes you enjoy your meal.

00:34:22.480 --> 00:34:24.040
He'll tuck you in tonight.

00:34:25.480 --> 00:34:26.480
What the hell is this?

00:34:27.800 --> 00:34:29.600
That's it. Restaurant is closed.

00:34:34.720 --> 00:34:36.720
It's a weird question,

00:34:36.800 --> 00:34:37.680
but I…

00:34:40.080 --> 00:34:42.680
I need to know if…

00:34:43.720 --> 00:34:44.560
Well…

00:34:46.720 --> 00:34:49.400
Was it really Babakar
who stole the necklace 25 years ago?

00:34:49.480 --> 00:34:50.320
What?

00:34:51.760 --> 00:34:54.880
A necklace worth millions was stolen

00:34:54.960 --> 00:34:57.560
and funding for the foundation
is in trouble.

00:34:57.640 --> 00:35:01.560
And you piss me off with an old story?
Of course he stole the necklace from us!

00:35:07.040 --> 00:35:09.440
Forgive me. I'm sorry, darling.

00:35:09.520 --> 00:35:11.680
No, it's my fault.

00:35:11.760 --> 00:35:14.280
I keep taking hits.
Everyone wants my head.

00:35:14.960 --> 00:35:16.040
Coming from you…

00:35:18.520 --> 00:35:20.480
Your father can fend for himself.

00:35:27.480 --> 00:35:28.560
You're with me.

00:35:32.280 --> 00:35:33.240
You're with me?

00:35:36.000 --> 00:35:37.400
Yes.

00:35:49.480 --> 00:35:51.560
Stop slacking, come on!

00:35:56.280 --> 00:35:57.200
There he is.

00:36:00.000 --> 00:36:01.360
Come on. Let's do this.

00:36:10.600 --> 00:36:11.640
Here!

00:36:26.200 --> 00:36:27.080
Tonight.

00:36:33.720 --> 00:36:35.960
You're in love with me.

00:36:39.920 --> 00:36:40.800
How is he?

00:36:46.760 --> 00:36:47.760
Can I see him?

00:36:50.840 --> 00:36:51.680
Thank you.

00:36:58.520 --> 00:36:59.760
How's it going, man?

00:37:03.640 --> 00:37:04.880
I think she digs you.

00:37:09.160 --> 00:37:10.360
You found the book?

00:37:12.800 --> 00:37:13.640
Cool.

00:37:17.920 --> 00:37:19.360
Can I ask you something?

00:37:20.240 --> 00:37:21.080
Anything.

00:37:23.480 --> 00:37:24.960
Don't care how you do it,

00:37:26.080 --> 00:37:27.440
but make my wife smile.

00:37:30.080 --> 00:37:31.680
I won't be able to anymore.

00:37:36.320 --> 00:37:37.160
Promise.

00:37:39.280 --> 00:37:40.120
OK.

00:37:42.840 --> 00:37:44.160
Thanks for the book.

00:37:44.920 --> 00:37:47.920
I got what I needed.
I need to avenge my father.

00:38:06.720 --> 00:38:08.520
It was a pleasure meeting you.

00:38:12.040 --> 00:38:13.360
Hang in there, Djibril.

00:38:17.200 --> 00:38:18.040
Thank you.

00:38:39.520 --> 00:38:40.440
Good night.

00:38:54.640 --> 00:38:56.640
ARSÈNE LUPIN IS IN PRISON

00:39:03.200 --> 00:39:04.080
Raoul.

00:39:04.160 --> 00:39:06.480
Put down your book.
Turn off the light now, please.

00:39:11.400 --> 00:39:12.240
Come on.

00:39:16.120 --> 00:39:16.960
Good night.

00:39:46.360 --> 00:39:47.480
Let's go.

00:39:55.600 --> 00:39:58.320
If you find a clue in Harry Potter…
call us.

00:40:01.080 --> 00:40:03.280
-See you tomorrow.
-Give me a lift?

00:40:03.360 --> 00:40:04.600
-With pleasure.
-Cool.

00:40:05.560 --> 00:40:06.560
See you tomorrow.

00:40:23.280 --> 00:40:26.800
DECEASED

00:40:36.240 --> 00:40:38.120
No!

00:40:39.320 --> 00:40:42.360
Help! Guard!

00:41:02.840 --> 00:41:03.960
So, all good? Done?

00:41:05.080 --> 00:41:07.880
-No trouble?
-No, on the contrary.

00:41:07.960 --> 00:41:09.080
It was too easy.

00:41:10.480 --> 00:41:12.480
The bastard wasn't in his cell.

00:41:13.440 --> 00:41:14.920
Don't know how he did it.

00:41:16.520 --> 00:41:18.600
I found him in the showers.

00:41:20.000 --> 00:41:21.200
He'd hanged himself.

00:41:48.240 --> 00:41:51.680
"Illusion is probably the most subtle
of all the arts."

00:41:53.360 --> 00:41:55.160
"It requires some finesse."

00:42:07.360 --> 00:42:09.560
"Sometimes, a fair amount of courage…"

00:42:20.720 --> 00:42:22.920
"Eventually, the means do not matter."

00:42:23.480 --> 00:42:25.280
"For only the outcome matters."

00:42:32.160 --> 00:42:34.960
-Given his condition, no need for it.
-Yeah.

00:42:35.040 --> 00:42:36.080
"And, of course,

00:42:36.760 --> 00:42:38.560
the thrill of tricking everyone."

00:42:39.400 --> 00:42:42.080
THE ESCAPE OF ARSÈNE LUPIN

00:43:28.680 --> 00:43:29.520
Hello, sir.

00:43:37.760 --> 00:43:38.760
Excuse me.

00:43:58.000 --> 00:43:58.840
Assane.

00:44:00.120 --> 00:44:01.480
Assane!

00:44:01.560 --> 00:44:03.600
I know you framed my father 25 years ago.

00:44:07.440 --> 00:44:08.800
What did you do to him?

00:44:10.760 --> 00:44:11.600
Assane…

00:44:12.680 --> 00:44:14.040
What did you do to him?

00:44:21.120 --> 00:44:22.840
Made him sign the confession.

00:44:27.840 --> 00:44:30.560
-But I am innocent!
-Innocent or not, that is not the issue.

00:44:30.640 --> 00:44:32.640
-Of course it is!
-Trust me.

00:44:32.720 --> 00:44:35.080
Better guilty and free
than innocent in jail.

00:44:36.440 --> 00:44:38.840
So sign. Think of your son.

00:44:41.880 --> 00:44:42.880
For Assane.

00:44:48.600 --> 00:44:51.320
It was supposed to earn him
a reduced sentence.

00:44:53.200 --> 00:44:56.560
I was told the judge
would be receptive to your situation.

00:44:57.920 --> 00:45:00.520
A Senegalese immigrant
raising his son alone in France.

00:45:01.760 --> 00:45:03.680
But the judge was so strict.

00:45:05.720 --> 00:45:08.480
Your father didn't accept it.
He hanged himself.

00:45:09.560 --> 00:45:11.280
That confession was his doom.

00:45:12.320 --> 00:45:13.160
I was naive.

00:45:15.840 --> 00:45:17.520
There were arrangements.

00:45:17.600 --> 00:45:19.920
Arrangements are only good
for people like you.

00:45:20.720 --> 00:45:22.040
Never people like my father.

00:45:23.200 --> 00:45:25.280
After his death, I helped you.

00:45:25.360 --> 00:45:26.240
I helped you.

00:45:27.560 --> 00:45:28.600
From a distance.

00:45:30.520 --> 00:45:32.000
From a distance, but I helped.

00:45:35.080 --> 00:45:36.160
It was you?

00:45:38.240 --> 00:45:39.760
The generous donor?

00:45:40.680 --> 00:45:41.520
It was you?

00:45:46.440 --> 00:45:48.920
I felt responsible for your situation.

00:45:50.040 --> 00:45:52.040
I wanted to earn your forgiveness.

00:45:53.720 --> 00:45:55.800
-Your father…
-Good old Babakar!

00:45:56.400 --> 00:46:00.680
You accuse him, drive him to suicide,
and then you ease your conscience!

00:46:00.760 --> 00:46:01.800
I didn't accuse him!

00:46:03.880 --> 00:46:06.360
A police officer swore that he'd help him!

00:46:06.440 --> 00:46:09.000
-That's all! He lied.
-Which police officer?

00:46:11.000 --> 00:46:12.240
Which police officer?

00:46:12.720 --> 00:46:14.680
-It was so long ago--
-No!

00:46:15.280 --> 00:46:16.400
Which police officer?

00:46:18.160 --> 00:46:19.000
His name.

00:46:24.920 --> 00:46:27.240
-Dumont. His name was Dumont.
-Guard.

00:46:27.320 --> 00:46:28.440
Lt. Dumont.

00:46:32.200 --> 00:46:35.160
Dumont used my father's trust in you
to frame him.

00:46:37.600 --> 00:46:39.600
-Why did he do that?
-I don't know.

00:46:40.560 --> 00:46:42.160
I searched for a long time.

00:46:44.640 --> 00:46:45.480
Assane.

00:46:47.120 --> 00:46:47.960
I swear.

00:47:06.520 --> 00:47:08.760
-Where are you going?
-He's lost.

00:47:08.840 --> 00:47:10.760
That's not a bad costume!

00:47:10.840 --> 00:47:13.360
-Turn around.
-I got it. I know. He took the wrong exit.

00:47:13.440 --> 00:47:15.880
-Service exit is that way!
-Gentlemen, be polite.

00:47:15.960 --> 00:47:18.560
I'll tell the principal
how you treat new students.

00:47:21.120 --> 00:47:24.320
Excuse them. They were born rich,
but with shit for brains.

00:47:25.280 --> 00:47:26.200
Benjamin Ferel.

00:47:27.480 --> 00:47:29.320
-Assane Diop.
-Nice to meet you.

00:49:06.680 --> 00:49:08.120
Can I ask you something?

00:49:10.040 --> 00:49:11.520
Don't care how you do it,

00:49:12.720 --> 00:49:14.160
but make my wife smile.

00:49:39.520 --> 00:49:43.120
LT. GABRIEL DUMONT
PARIS REGIONAL POLICE

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:14.960
[gardien] Noyau !

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:16.800
[musique suspense]

00:00:25.040 --> 00:00:28.400
[cris des détenus]

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:50.440
[gardien] Ton nouveau coloc.

00:00:56.800 --> 00:00:58.040
T'es là pour quoi, toi ?

00:01:27.320 --> 00:01:30.640
- [Assane] Tu plaisantes.
- [Benjamin] Je t'aurais pas appelé.

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:35.720
- C'est pas possible, vérifie encore.
- Toute la nuit, je l'ai vérifié !

00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:41.520
Fermoir original. Sertissage original.
Aucune marque sur les pierres.

00:01:41.600 --> 00:01:44.600
Je te garantis que ce collier
n'a jamais été démonté.

00:01:45.160 --> 00:01:49.200
Ça veut dire que les pierres éparpillées
dans le monde, c'est de la connerie.

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:52.320
Ce collier n'a jamais quitté
le coffre des Pellegrini.

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:54.160
- Pourquoi mentir ?
- Je sais pas.

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:56.480
Ils ont peut-être menti sur tout le reste.

00:01:56.560 --> 00:01:58.880
Y compris sur l'accusation
contre mon père.

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:01.720
Vingt-cinq ans que je me dis
que mon père est un voleur.

00:02:02.720 --> 00:02:05.800
- Vingt-cinq ans que je me plante.
- Doucement, Assane.

00:02:06.480 --> 00:02:08.280
T'as le collier, tu t'en es sorti.

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:10.880
- On se fout du reste.
- La vérité, on s'en fout ?

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:12.920
Je dis pas ça, mais bon…

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:17.360
Tu avais dit qu'après ce collier,
tu arrêterais.

00:02:17.440 --> 00:02:19.120
Que Raoul a besoin de son père.

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:22.240
- Pense à lui.
- [Assane] Je fais que ça.

00:02:23.600 --> 00:02:25.640
Il doit savoir qui était son grand-père.

00:02:27.760 --> 00:02:28.840
Sors-moi les pierres.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:32.120
- Assane…
- Je sais ce que je fais.

00:02:34.640 --> 00:02:35.960
Vous faites quoi ?

00:02:37.720 --> 00:02:38.800
Rien de spécial.

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:45.320
- Tu planques un truc.
- Moi ?

00:02:48.440 --> 00:02:49.400
Pas du tout.

00:02:50.200 --> 00:02:52.520
- Il me croit pas !
- Les enfants…

00:02:52.600 --> 00:02:54.600
[cris joyeux d'enfants]

00:03:06.520 --> 00:03:08.440
- [on frappe]
- Police, ouvre !

00:03:11.200 --> 00:03:14.120
- [coups forts]
- Inspecteur Dumont, ouvre !

00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:26.360
M'oblige pas à défoncer la porte.

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:32.200
Assieds-toi.

00:03:41.200 --> 00:03:43.640
- T'as quel âge ?
- Seize ans.

00:03:45.240 --> 00:03:47.720
- Tu vis seul, ici ?
- Je vis avec ma mère.

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:50.760
- Elle va revenir.
- Ah bon ?

00:03:58.080 --> 00:03:59.480
On va l'attendre, ta mère.

00:04:11.200 --> 00:04:13.600
Prépare un sac,
je t'emmène aux services sociaux.

00:04:17.640 --> 00:04:18.680
T'as entendu ?

00:04:19.840 --> 00:04:21.800
[en criant] Allez, là ! Dépêche-toi !

00:04:53.480 --> 00:04:54.560
[musique suspense]

00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:09.880
Bon, qu'est-ce que tu fous ?

00:05:37.320 --> 00:05:39.680
Va falloir bosser ta technique d'évasion !

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:53.360
- [Juliette] Bonjour, maman.
- Bonjour.

00:05:53.440 --> 00:05:56.320
Je passe en coup de vent,
faut que j'aille à la fondation.

00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:58.480
J'ai appris, pour le collier de ton père.

00:05:59.040 --> 00:06:02.840
C'est une copie, qu'ils ont retrouvée.
Ça doit le rendre dingue, tout ça.

00:06:03.520 --> 00:06:05.640
Ça a l'air de te faire beaucoup de peine.

00:06:07.520 --> 00:06:09.640
T'inquiète pas, la police a une piste.

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:12.280
Selon les journaux,
mais la plupart sont à lui.

00:06:12.360 --> 00:06:14.240
- On peut douter.
- [Juliette soupire]

00:06:14.320 --> 00:06:16.520
- [sonnerie]
- Le collier a encore disparu.

00:06:16.600 --> 00:06:19.560
- Pas de chance.
- [Juliette] Pas de chance, non.

00:06:19.640 --> 00:06:22.400
Cette histoire l'avait beaucoup contrarié,
à l'époque.

00:06:22.480 --> 00:06:24.280
Ça va être pire, cette fois.

00:06:24.960 --> 00:06:26.160
Et toi, tu vas bien ?

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:28.400
Je me fane lentement mais sûrement.

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:31.440
Dans cette prison dorée
offerte par ton père.

00:06:31.520 --> 00:06:33.600
C'est lui qui a choisi les orchidées.

00:06:34.360 --> 00:06:36.800
- On a évité les chrysanthèmes.
- Arrête.

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:39.960
- Il te déteste pas, maman.
- Non, je lui fais peur.

00:06:40.040 --> 00:06:41.800
Je sais où sont les cadavres.

00:06:42.480 --> 00:06:44.400
Fais attention à toi, Juliette.

00:06:44.480 --> 00:06:46.520
Il t'adore, tu l'adores, mais…

00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:47.920
c'est lui-même qui le dit.

00:06:48.640 --> 00:06:50.400
On est avec lui ou contre lui.

00:06:52.520 --> 00:06:53.600
Au revoir, maman.

00:06:54.160 --> 00:06:55.240
Au revoir, Juliette.

00:07:01.720 --> 00:07:03.280
Au revoir, François.

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:05.880
Mademoiselle Pellegrini ?
On a déposé ça pour vous.

00:07:05.960 --> 00:07:07.720
- Ah, merci.
- Avec plaisir.

00:07:28.200 --> 00:07:30.040
- Au revoir.
- Au revoir. Merci.

00:07:35.800 --> 00:07:37.800
À point, sans oignons.

00:07:37.880 --> 00:07:39.320
Voilà, merci.

00:07:39.840 --> 00:07:41.360
Oui, madame. C'est ça.

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:42.960
À point, sans oignons.

00:07:43.040 --> 00:07:43.920
Merci.

00:07:47.080 --> 00:07:49.240
[musique rythmée]

00:08:20.240 --> 00:08:22.000
Vous êtes pressé, moi aussi.

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:24.640
Vous voulez combien ?

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:27.160
Mon prix à moi, c'est zéro.

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:28.680
Je veux pas d'argent.

00:08:31.080 --> 00:08:32.600
Je veux des réponses.

00:08:33.640 --> 00:08:36.920
- Pourquoi j'entends plus rien, là ?
- Il a la main sur le micro.

00:08:37.000 --> 00:08:38.720
- Réglez-moi ça !
- Je suis dessus.

00:08:38.800 --> 00:08:40.720
Réglez ça, je veux les entendre.

00:08:40.800 --> 00:08:43.840
À toutes les unités,
le voleur du Louvre est sur zone.

00:08:43.920 --> 00:08:46.720
Personne n'intervient
avant qu'il ne bouge. Compris ?

00:08:46.800 --> 00:08:48.440
J'avais dit pas de police.

00:08:49.280 --> 00:08:52.520
- C'est toi qui as volé le collier ?
- Je pose les questions.

00:08:53.240 --> 00:08:56.360
- Pourquoi vous avez menti ?
- Menti ? Sur quoi ?

00:08:56.440 --> 00:08:59.400
Ce collier. Il a jamais été démonté.

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:02.120
Donc mon père vous l'a jamais volé.

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:04.480
C'est vrai.

00:09:06.120 --> 00:09:08.120
Il n'a jamais été démonté, oui.

00:09:09.280 --> 00:09:12.880
Avec mon père, on a eu l'idée
des joyaux dispersés dans le monde

00:09:12.960 --> 00:09:14.960
pour faire le buzz avant la vente.

00:09:15.520 --> 00:09:19.200
Papa l'a racheté intact il y a cinq ans
à un joaillier en Afrique du Sud.

00:09:20.520 --> 00:09:22.760
- Ça tient pas, ça.
- Je te promets, Assane.

00:09:22.840 --> 00:09:25.160
- Regarde-moi, tu me connais.
- Arrête.

00:09:25.240 --> 00:09:27.840
Putain, ils se connaissent !
C'est de la connivence.

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:31.720
J'en suis sûr !
Pellegrini nous la fait à l'envers.

00:09:31.800 --> 00:09:34.200
Belkacem, je veux entendre,
tu te rapproches !

00:09:35.080 --> 00:09:37.000
Mets-toi entre eux et la sortie.

00:09:37.080 --> 00:09:40.000
[Juliette] Si mon père l'apprend,
tu es un homme mort.

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:41.960
Rends-moi le collier.

00:09:42.040 --> 00:09:45.040
- Je dirai rien aux flics.
- Dis que mon père était innocent.

00:09:45.120 --> 00:09:46.960
J'adorerais pouvoir te dire ça,

00:09:47.040 --> 00:09:49.080
mais il a signé des aveux.

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:54.360
Tu connais pas ton père.

00:10:02.680 --> 00:10:05.400
[Rosemary Clooney "Sway"]

00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:06.640
OK, il bouge !

00:10:06.720 --> 00:10:09.520
À toutes les unités,
on se le ramène au chaud !

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:11.200
[policier] Arrête !

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:13.400
Attends !

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:14.560
Chope-le !

00:10:14.640 --> 00:10:16.800
Il s'est barré avec son vélo. Chopez-le !

00:10:18.680 --> 00:10:20.360
[policier] Il est là, il est là !

00:10:21.680 --> 00:10:23.520
[cris des policiers]

00:10:27.680 --> 00:10:30.080
- Le laissez pas se barrer !
- On est dessus.

00:10:30.160 --> 00:10:31.640
Cette fois, on se l'attrape !

00:10:37.240 --> 00:10:39.960
Il est allé direction Vavin.
Chopez-le à la sortie.

00:10:43.000 --> 00:10:44.280
C'est quoi, ce bordel ?

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:53.680
Comment il fait, putain ?

00:10:53.760 --> 00:10:55.280
Les gars, vers Sénat !

00:10:56.400 --> 00:10:58.000
C'est pas possible, merde !

00:10:59.040 --> 00:11:01.200
[Belkacem]
Il se dirige vers l'Observatoire.

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:03.960
Sortie six,
rue de l'Observatoire, on y va !

00:11:04.040 --> 00:11:05.600
[sirènes de police]

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:10.880
[policier] Arrête-toi !

00:11:11.920 --> 00:11:14.040
Couche-toi ! Viens là, putain.

00:11:14.640 --> 00:11:16.880
Fais voir tes mains ! Tes mains !

00:11:17.600 --> 00:11:18.560
C'est pas lui.

00:11:18.640 --> 00:11:20.680
Un burger à point sans oignons ?

00:11:20.760 --> 00:11:23.480
- [Belkacem] C'est pas lui !
- [policiers] Bouge plus !

00:11:25.320 --> 00:11:26.960
Merde, putain !

00:11:27.440 --> 00:11:29.040
Enlève ton masque !

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:32.000
- Fais voir ton visage.
- Bouclez le parc.

00:11:32.080 --> 00:11:33.480
Personne ne sort !

00:11:34.520 --> 00:11:37.480
C'est pas possible, il est où ? Merde !

00:12:16.240 --> 00:12:18.240
[il inspire]

00:12:33.680 --> 00:12:36.080
[Babakar] "Mon fils, j'ai honte.

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:38.760
Je suis coupable de ce dont on m'accuse.

00:12:38.840 --> 00:12:42.040
Je voulais t'offrir une vie meilleure.
J'ai échoué.

00:12:42.640 --> 00:12:45.520
Alors j'espère que tu me pardonneras.

00:12:45.600 --> 00:12:46.880
Mais souviens-toi,

00:12:46.960 --> 00:12:50.040
la vérité se trouvera toujours
dans les 'bibliotèques'.

00:12:50.680 --> 00:12:52.800
Ne 'comet' pas les mêmes erreurs que moi.

00:12:53.400 --> 00:12:54.400
Je t'aime.

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:56.240
Papa."

00:12:57.600 --> 00:13:00.040
De Gaulle avec un seul "L" ?

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:03.200
Sois attentif, Assane.
L'orthographe, c'est essentiel.

00:13:03.280 --> 00:13:05.200
Si ta mère te voyait !

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:12.800
[musique suspense]

00:13:46.960 --> 00:13:50.040
- J'en fais toujours, des fautes.
- Toi et moi, oui.

00:13:50.600 --> 00:13:53.480
Mon père, jamais.
Encore moins deux de suite.

00:13:53.560 --> 00:13:55.920
- Ah oui ? Et ?
- Regarde.

00:13:57.520 --> 00:13:59.560
- "Comet", "bibliotèques".
- Oui.

00:13:59.640 --> 00:14:01.160
- Et ?
- J'ai regardé.

00:14:02.160 --> 00:14:05.640
Avec mon père en prison,
un détenu s'appelait Étienne Comet.

00:14:06.200 --> 00:14:09.560
C-O-M-E-T.
Et tu sais où il était affecté ?

00:14:10.800 --> 00:14:12.800
- À la bibliothèque ?
- Exactement.

00:14:12.880 --> 00:14:15.560
[Benjamin siffle] Attends. Ça, Assane…

00:14:15.640 --> 00:14:17.880
Ça s'appelle… un hasard.

00:14:19.120 --> 00:14:22.400
- T'es sérieux ?
- Deux fautes et il y a un message caché ?

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:25.400
- Tu vas chercher loin.
- Tu te rends pas compte.

00:14:27.880 --> 00:14:29.320
J'ai ça depuis des années.

00:14:30.040 --> 00:14:34.040
Vingt-cinq ans que je peux prouver
l'innocence de mon père, grâce à ce Comet.

00:14:34.600 --> 00:14:35.600
Et j'ai rien fait.

00:14:40.200 --> 00:14:41.120
T'as raison.

00:14:42.240 --> 00:14:45.000
T'as un doute, va au bout de ton truc,
va voir ce Comet.

00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:47.640
- Il est où ?
- Toujours en prison.

00:14:48.200 --> 00:14:51.080
- Demande un parloir.
- Il est malade, il bouge pas.

00:14:52.400 --> 00:14:54.800
- Eh bien…
- Je vais me débrouiller autrement.

00:14:57.640 --> 00:14:58.760
- Non !
- Si.

00:14:58.840 --> 00:15:00.680
- Non !
- Tu m'as dit : "Va au bout."

00:15:00.760 --> 00:15:01.800
Je vais au bout.

00:15:03.080 --> 00:15:04.240
Je dois voir ce Comet.

00:15:05.600 --> 00:15:08.280
Fait chier, putain ! Assane !

00:15:08.840 --> 00:15:09.720
Attends !

00:15:10.400 --> 00:15:11.360
Attends !

00:15:19.520 --> 00:15:21.160
[buzz d'ouverture de grille]

00:15:31.480 --> 00:15:32.920
Parloir pour Djibril Traoré.

00:15:38.360 --> 00:15:39.320
Salut, cousin.

00:15:42.040 --> 00:15:43.040
Assieds-toi.

00:15:44.320 --> 00:15:46.480
D'où t'as vu qu'on est cousins,
toi et moi ?

00:15:47.960 --> 00:15:48.920
J'ai pas de cousin.

00:15:50.120 --> 00:15:51.480
Maintenant, t'en as un.

00:15:52.320 --> 00:15:54.440
Et ton cousin, il a un cadeau pour toi.

00:15:57.480 --> 00:15:59.240
Toi, tu sors…

00:16:00.440 --> 00:16:01.680
et je rentre à ta place.

00:16:02.520 --> 00:16:04.120
[il explose de rire]

00:16:09.320 --> 00:16:10.760
Non, mais attends.

00:16:10.840 --> 00:16:12.400
T'es complètement con ou quoi ?

00:16:13.200 --> 00:16:15.480
Ah si, je sais ! En fait…

00:16:15.560 --> 00:16:18.120
les surveillants
ne vont s'apercevoir de rien

00:16:18.200 --> 00:16:19.960
parce que toi et moi,

00:16:20.040 --> 00:16:22.440
on se ressemble
comme de vrais jumeaux.

00:16:25.120 --> 00:16:26.320
[sonnerie montre]

00:16:26.400 --> 00:16:29.240
[sonnerie prison]

00:16:29.320 --> 00:16:30.240
Ça y est.

00:16:32.680 --> 00:16:33.800
Les gardes ont changé.

00:16:39.160 --> 00:16:40.720
Et les autres détenus ?

00:16:40.800 --> 00:16:43.160
T'étais en quarantaine avec les nouveaux.

00:16:43.840 --> 00:16:46.480
Mais ce soir, tu vas en cellule.

00:16:47.600 --> 00:16:49.360
Et en prison, personne te connaît.

00:16:50.160 --> 00:16:52.680
Oui, mais…
t'oublierais pas un détail, non ?

00:16:56.360 --> 00:16:58.520
Oh merde, les menottes…

00:16:58.600 --> 00:17:01.040
"Oh merde, les menottes."

00:17:01.120 --> 00:17:02.520
Je suis vraiment con.

00:17:04.320 --> 00:17:06.080
Comment j'ai fait pour oublier ça ?

00:17:12.120 --> 00:17:14.840
- Tu connais le coup des menottes ?
- Le coup de quoi ?

00:17:16.440 --> 00:17:17.800
Maintenant, tu connais.

00:17:19.520 --> 00:17:21.200
Surveillant ! On a fini.

00:17:21.760 --> 00:17:25.440
Hé ! Je sais pourquoi t'es là.
Si tu trafiques, même un joint,

00:17:25.520 --> 00:17:26.960
je te retrouve.

00:17:28.120 --> 00:17:30.400
Je t'ai fait sortir,
je peux te faire revenir.

00:17:34.160 --> 00:17:36.160
- Salut, cousin.
- Allez-y.

00:17:38.560 --> 00:17:39.400
[garde] Noyau.

00:17:39.480 --> 00:17:41.360
[buzz d'ouverture de grille]

00:17:50.680 --> 00:17:52.440
Embrasse tata pour moi.

00:17:52.520 --> 00:17:53.920
[garde] Noyau.

00:18:00.880 --> 00:18:02.440
[buzz d'ouverture de grille]

00:18:06.680 --> 00:18:10.080
[brouhaha des détenus]

00:18:36.800 --> 00:18:39.360
[travailleur social]
Au début, c'est difficile, ici.

00:18:40.120 --> 00:18:41.680
Mais tu vas t'y faire.

00:18:42.520 --> 00:18:44.520
Nous respectons les croyances de chacun.

00:18:46.880 --> 00:18:50.040
À titre personnel, il y a une lecture
qui m'a apporté souvent…

00:18:50.120 --> 00:18:51.920
comment dire… des réponses.

00:18:52.840 --> 00:18:53.920
Et du réconfort.

00:18:59.480 --> 00:19:00.960
Sois le bienvenu, mon garçon.

00:19:09.880 --> 00:19:13.040
[Laugier] Madame Pellegrini,
quelque chose me chiffonne.

00:19:14.040 --> 00:19:17.960
On n'avait pas le son, mais à l'image
on aurait dit que le suspect et vous…

00:19:19.200 --> 00:19:20.760
vous vous connaissiez.

00:19:22.320 --> 00:19:26.120
Et moi, j'ai l'impression
que vous me parlez comme à une suspecte.

00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:29.760
- Suis-je mise en cause ?
- Non, bien sûr. Pas du tout.

00:19:29.840 --> 00:19:32.920
Si c'est le cas, aucun problème.
Mettez-moi en garde à vue.

00:19:33.480 --> 00:19:35.960
J'envoie mes avocats
et vous serez mis à pied.

00:19:36.040 --> 00:19:38.360
- On fait comme ça ?
- Attendez…

00:19:38.440 --> 00:19:42.680
Je vous conseille de changer de ton.
Et de vous concentrer sur votre enquête.

00:19:43.440 --> 00:19:46.760
Je demande juste
ce que vous vous êtes dit, j'ai le droit ?

00:19:47.760 --> 00:19:49.240
Absolument.

00:19:51.160 --> 00:19:52.360
Je lui ai dit que…

00:19:53.680 --> 00:19:56.600
le policier chargé de l'affaire
est un abruti

00:19:56.680 --> 00:19:58.640
qui m'a ramené un collier en plastique.

00:20:01.120 --> 00:20:02.240
Vous ne notez plus ?

00:20:05.680 --> 00:20:07.480
Retrouvez notre collier, capitaine.

00:20:09.520 --> 00:20:11.920
Vous ne voulez pas
décevoir vos supérieurs, non ?

00:20:13.320 --> 00:20:15.520
- Non, madame.
- Très bien.

00:20:18.640 --> 00:20:19.640
[Juliette] Merci.

00:20:27.840 --> 00:20:31.160
[annonce inaudible au haut-parleur]

00:20:33.960 --> 00:20:37.080
- Je t'ai fait du café, si tu veux.
- Merci.

00:20:40.480 --> 00:20:43.480
[brouhaha des détenus]

00:21:00.480 --> 00:21:02.200
[détenu] Hé, le nouveau !

00:21:02.760 --> 00:21:04.640
Ouais, ouais !

00:21:06.160 --> 00:21:07.080
[détenus] Envoie !

00:21:08.280 --> 00:21:09.800
[détenus] Ouais !

00:21:09.880 --> 00:21:12.560
[applaudissements]

00:21:14.480 --> 00:21:17.400
[conversation inaudible]

00:21:21.840 --> 00:21:23.200
Salut.

00:21:24.760 --> 00:21:26.920
Vous connaissez un mec
qui s'appelle Comet ?

00:21:27.520 --> 00:21:28.760
Étienne Comet ?

00:21:30.080 --> 00:21:33.280
- Qu'est-ce que tu lui veux ?
- Rien. On a un pote en commun.

00:21:34.400 --> 00:21:35.520
C'est qui, ton pote ?

00:21:39.480 --> 00:21:42.200
Je vais arrêter.
C'est pas bon pour le souffle.

00:21:43.840 --> 00:21:45.080
Ça vous intéresse ?

00:21:50.360 --> 00:21:51.520
Cellule 241.

00:21:56.120 --> 00:21:58.360
Renseigne-toi sur lui.
Je veux tout savoir.

00:22:29.320 --> 00:22:31.840
[Guédira] Vincent,
c'est quoi, ta version du vol ?

00:22:36.240 --> 00:22:39.440
[Vincent] Il s'appelait Luis Perenna.
Je l'avais jamais vu avant.

00:22:50.560 --> 00:22:52.800
[gardienne] 241, Comet, Leroy.

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:56.280
- [homme] Surveillant ?
- Oui, j'arrive.

00:22:57.240 --> 00:22:59.600
- Il est où, Étienne ?
- À l'infirmerie.

00:22:59.680 --> 00:23:03.160
- Il revient quand ?
- Vu son état, il reviendra pas.

00:23:03.240 --> 00:23:04.480
Vas-y, merci.

00:23:17.800 --> 00:23:19.080
T'es qui, toi ?

00:23:20.520 --> 00:23:23.360
- T'es qui ?
- Djibril. Djibril Traoré.

00:23:25.160 --> 00:23:29.080
Djibril me devait 1 000 € de came.
C'est toi qui me les dois et t'as 3 jours.

00:23:29.160 --> 00:23:32.240
- Trois jours ?
- Quoi, c'est trop long, Djibril ? Hein ?

00:23:34.440 --> 00:23:35.760
Non, c'est bien.

00:23:35.840 --> 00:23:37.320
- Ouais.
- Trois jours.

00:23:38.440 --> 00:23:41.120
- [gardienne] Qu'est-ce qui se passe, là ?
- Rien.

00:23:44.080 --> 00:23:47.240
[il siffle la comptine "Alouette"]

00:23:53.320 --> 00:23:54.880
[on frappe]

00:23:56.200 --> 00:23:58.120
Il a déjà un pet de travers, celui-là.

00:23:58.200 --> 00:24:00.200
C'est bon, Marc. Je m'en occupe.

00:24:05.040 --> 00:24:06.120
Installez-vous.

00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:13.840
Alors, qu'est-ce que vous avez ?

00:24:14.560 --> 00:24:16.560
Ça a commencé par une douleur diffuse.

00:24:17.640 --> 00:24:19.200
J'ai pensé à une grossesse.

00:24:20.000 --> 00:24:21.240
Mais bon, c'est pas ça.

00:24:21.960 --> 00:24:24.840
- Probablement pas, effectivement.
- Et je me suis dit…

00:24:25.600 --> 00:24:29.600
Une petite nuit à l'infirmerie.
En observation. C'est plus prudent, non ?

00:24:32.400 --> 00:24:35.240
Bon, écoutez…
Je sais que c'est dur, au début.

00:24:36.520 --> 00:24:39.040
Mais vous allez vous habituer, hein ?

00:24:42.120 --> 00:24:43.200
Et pour ma nuit ici ?

00:24:44.360 --> 00:24:45.840
Là, va falloir trouver mieux.

00:24:45.920 --> 00:24:47.560
- Ah ouais ?
- Ouais.

00:24:50.680 --> 00:24:53.600
- [Guédira] T'as deux minutes ?
- Je vais voir le patron.

00:24:53.680 --> 00:24:55.840
Deux minutes.
Faut que je te montre un truc.

00:25:00.400 --> 00:25:01.440
Regarde.

00:25:02.840 --> 00:25:03.920
"Paul Sernine."

00:25:04.840 --> 00:25:05.840
"Luis Perenna."

00:25:07.640 --> 00:25:10.320
- Mais tu fais quoi, là ?
- Tu vois pas ?

00:25:12.640 --> 00:25:14.200
Deux anagrammes d'Arsène Lupin.

00:25:16.760 --> 00:25:18.320
- Et ?
- C'est logique, en fait.

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:21.000
Il y a un lien entre le voleur
et Arsène Lupin.

00:25:21.080 --> 00:25:24.000
C'est un angle à étudier.
J'en parle à Laugier ?

00:25:25.240 --> 00:25:26.920
Ouais, très bonne idée.

00:25:27.560 --> 00:25:30.720
Si tu veux passer pour un con.
En plus, il est de bonne humeur.

00:25:30.800 --> 00:25:32.520
Sérieux, c'est quoi, ça ?

00:25:32.600 --> 00:25:34.760
Ça va être quoi, après ? D'Artagnan ?

00:25:34.840 --> 00:25:37.040
Remets-toi au taf et laisse-nous avancer.

00:25:38.080 --> 00:25:41.080
[Laugier] On peut pas sortir
une meilleure image ?

00:25:41.160 --> 00:25:44.640
Le mec, il met un costume de coursier
et on est morts !

00:25:44.720 --> 00:25:47.320
Il est en train de nous balader, le gars !

00:25:47.400 --> 00:25:51.440
On est nulle part. On est des nazes !
C'est n'importe quoi, cette enquête !

00:25:53.200 --> 00:25:54.520
[brouhaha des détenus]

00:26:06.480 --> 00:26:08.320
- Dis-moi.
- Tu veux quoi, toi ?

00:26:09.680 --> 00:26:12.960
- Il passait la came comment, Djibril ?
- En quoi ça te regarde ?

00:26:13.720 --> 00:26:16.920
- Simple curiosité.
- T'es con ou quoi ? Il l'avalait.

00:26:17.000 --> 00:26:20.200
- Du coup, il devait se la sortir du cul.
- Voilà, c'est ça.

00:26:20.280 --> 00:26:22.800
C'est là que tu vas te le mettre,
ton pognon.

00:26:24.160 --> 00:26:25.760
Ma parole, il veut mourir, lui.

00:26:27.360 --> 00:26:30.360
[cris des détenus]

00:26:39.640 --> 00:26:40.760
[infirmière] Et voilà.

00:26:42.720 --> 00:26:45.000
Vous vous êtes fait ça tout seul,
j'imagine ?

00:26:45.080 --> 00:26:47.680
C'est ça, accident bête.
Je me rasais et…

00:26:48.520 --> 00:26:50.120
- ça a dérapé.
- Ah…

00:26:58.240 --> 00:27:00.560
Bon, je vous garde pour cette nuit.

00:27:02.000 --> 00:27:03.400
Enfin !

00:27:04.520 --> 00:27:06.800
Va falloir vous faire des amis.
Ça sert, ici.

00:27:12.080 --> 00:27:13.080
[Assane] Bonne nuit.

00:27:30.360 --> 00:27:31.520
[il chuchote] Étienne ?

00:27:33.920 --> 00:27:34.800
Étienne ?

00:27:36.640 --> 00:27:37.640
Étienne.

00:27:38.640 --> 00:27:40.040
Je m'appelle Assane Diop.

00:27:41.960 --> 00:27:44.080
Mon père s'appelait Babakar Diop.

00:27:45.520 --> 00:27:47.040
Vous étiez en prison ensemble.

00:27:54.000 --> 00:27:54.840
Étienne ?

00:27:56.800 --> 00:28:00.200
- [faiblement] Babakar…
- Oui ! Tu t'en souviens ?

00:28:01.720 --> 00:28:03.040
Ouais, peut-être.

00:28:05.640 --> 00:28:08.680
- C'est lui qui avait tiré un collier ?
- Si. Enfin, non.

00:28:09.880 --> 00:28:11.360
C'est pour ça que je suis là.

00:28:11.440 --> 00:28:13.080
Il a été condamné à tort.

00:28:15.760 --> 00:28:17.480
Je connais pas ton père.

00:28:19.960 --> 00:28:21.000
Non.

00:28:21.800 --> 00:28:23.800
- Non, c'est pas possible.
- Si.

00:28:24.680 --> 00:28:25.520
Comment ça ?

00:28:26.560 --> 00:28:28.200
Il était seul en cellule.

00:28:29.320 --> 00:28:30.800
Toujours surveillé.

00:28:32.480 --> 00:28:36.880
Je l'ai vu qu'une fois
parce que je lui ai ramené un bouquin,

00:28:37.720 --> 00:28:39.720
comme je bossais à la bibli.

00:28:40.520 --> 00:28:41.400
Mais c'est tout.

00:28:43.320 --> 00:28:45.440
Non, il y a forcément autre chose.

00:28:46.000 --> 00:28:47.840
Un petit effort, s'il te plaît.

00:28:47.920 --> 00:28:48.960
Étienne…

00:28:52.120 --> 00:28:54.760
- Quand il m'a rendu le bouquin, il a dit…
- Oui ?

00:28:55.520 --> 00:28:58.240
Il m'a dit que si un jour,
quelqu'un venait de sa part,

00:29:00.080 --> 00:29:01.800
il voudrait que je lui donne.

00:29:03.840 --> 00:29:06.280
Il disait que toutes les réponses
étaient dedans.

00:29:07.560 --> 00:29:09.000
Tu l'as toujours, ce livre ?

00:29:11.360 --> 00:29:12.840
Peut-être bien, oui.

00:29:13.400 --> 00:29:15.280
Fouille dans mes affaires.

00:29:32.160 --> 00:29:35.320
[cloche]

00:29:44.880 --> 00:29:46.400
Tu joues pas avec les autres ?

00:29:51.800 --> 00:29:54.080
C'est arrivé ce matin,
de la part de ton père.

00:29:55.360 --> 00:29:57.720
Les gardiens l'ont trouvée
en vidant sa cellule.

00:30:10.200 --> 00:30:12.560
Tu as déjà entendu parler
du collège d'Andrésy ?

00:30:13.640 --> 00:30:15.760
Un des meilleurs collèges privés
de France.

00:30:16.840 --> 00:30:19.360
Quelqu'un tient
à ce que tu y ailles l'an prochain.

00:30:22.120 --> 00:30:24.160
Ce généreux donateur a tout payé.

00:30:27.520 --> 00:30:31.040
Assane… Là-bas,
tu vas recevoir une vraie éducation.

00:30:31.680 --> 00:30:33.160
Tu pourras devenir quelqu'un.

00:30:35.920 --> 00:30:39.200
Profites-en, c'est ta chance.
Rien n'est écrit.

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:42.880
Je suis content que ça te plaise.

00:30:42.960 --> 00:30:44.960
[musique mélancolique]

00:30:57.200 --> 00:30:59.200
[Babakar] "Mon fils, j'ai honte.

00:30:59.800 --> 00:31:02.360
Je suis coupable
de ce dont on m'accuse.

00:31:02.440 --> 00:31:04.680
Je voulais t'offrir une vie meilleure.

00:31:04.760 --> 00:31:05.880
J'ai échoué."

00:31:18.040 --> 00:31:19.720
- [gardien] 241.
- Oui.

00:31:23.240 --> 00:31:25.240
Des draps propres. Mieux qu'au Ritz !

00:31:25.320 --> 00:31:28.000
- Où sont les affaires d'Étienne ?
- Deuxième étagère.

00:31:31.600 --> 00:31:33.880
[conversation inaudible]

00:31:49.360 --> 00:31:51.120
- Bon courage.
- Auxi !

00:32:04.960 --> 00:32:06.600
[Claire] C'était bien, les SVT ?

00:32:10.240 --> 00:32:12.680
- Raoul ? Je te parle, chéri.
- Hein ?

00:32:12.760 --> 00:32:15.080
- Ton contrôle s'est bien passé ?
- Oui.

00:32:19.400 --> 00:32:21.680
- C'est le livre que t'a offert papa ?
- Oui.

00:32:25.200 --> 00:32:27.480
[Claire] Il a gribouillé toutes les pages.

00:32:30.360 --> 00:32:32.240
Tu préfères lire que la console ?

00:32:36.480 --> 00:32:37.560
Ben, dis donc…

00:32:41.320 --> 00:32:42.800
[musique suspense]

00:32:51.120 --> 00:32:52.080
"Suis."

00:32:57.720 --> 00:32:58.720
"Innocent."

00:33:30.800 --> 00:33:32.800
[coup métallique]

00:33:46.480 --> 00:33:48.080
"Je suis innocent,

00:33:48.200 --> 00:33:49.960
piégé par Anne…

00:33:51.040 --> 00:33:52.080
Pellegrini."

00:33:53.640 --> 00:33:54.600
[cri]

00:34:19.960 --> 00:34:21.840
Bogdan te souhaite bon appétit.

00:34:22.400 --> 00:34:24.040
Il viendra te border cette nuit.

00:34:24.120 --> 00:34:25.400
[cris]

00:34:25.480 --> 00:34:26.920
C'est quoi, ce bordel, là ?

00:34:27.800 --> 00:34:29.720
[gardien] Terminé, on ferme le restau.

00:34:34.680 --> 00:34:37.680
[Juliette] Ça va te paraître bizarre
comme question, mais je…

00:34:40.040 --> 00:34:43.000
J'ai besoin de savoir si…

00:34:43.640 --> 00:34:44.640
Enfin…

00:34:46.640 --> 00:34:49.400
C'est vraiment Babakar
qui nous a volé le collier ?

00:34:49.480 --> 00:34:50.480
Quoi ?

00:34:51.720 --> 00:34:54.880
La fondation est en danger
parce qu'on nous a volé un collier

00:34:54.960 --> 00:34:57.560
qui vaut des millions
et toi, tu viens m'emmerder

00:34:57.640 --> 00:34:59.800
avec une affaire vieille de 25 ans ?

00:34:59.880 --> 00:35:01.840
[en criant] Évidemment qu'il l'a volé !

00:35:07.040 --> 00:35:09.440
Pardonne-moi. Excuse-moi, ma chérie.

00:35:09.520 --> 00:35:11.760
Non, c'est moi.

00:35:11.840 --> 00:35:14.200
Je prends des coups,
tout le monde veut ma peau.

00:35:14.960 --> 00:35:16.160
Alors venant de toi…

00:35:18.440 --> 00:35:20.600
Mais ton vieux père
peut encore se défendre.

00:35:27.440 --> 00:35:28.880
Tu es avec moi.

00:35:32.280 --> 00:35:33.520
Tu es avec moi ?

00:35:36.840 --> 00:35:37.800
Oui.

00:35:49.480 --> 00:35:51.560
[détenu] Arrête de te branler, là !

00:35:56.240 --> 00:35:57.200
Téma, il est là.

00:36:00.000 --> 00:36:01.520
Vas-y, c'est parti.

00:36:10.600 --> 00:36:11.640
Là !

00:36:15.800 --> 00:36:17.800
[les détenus huent]

00:36:26.200 --> 00:36:27.360
Ce soir.

00:36:33.680 --> 00:36:35.960
C'est pas possible,
vous êtes amoureux de moi.

00:36:39.880 --> 00:36:40.960
Comment il va ?

00:36:46.800 --> 00:36:48.200
Je peux le voir ?

00:36:50.800 --> 00:36:51.840
Merci.

00:36:59.000 --> 00:37:00.280
Comment ça va, mon pote ?

00:37:03.520 --> 00:37:04.880
Je crois qu'elle te kiffe.

00:37:09.080 --> 00:37:10.360
Tu as trouvé le bouquin ?

00:37:12.720 --> 00:37:13.640
Cool.

00:37:17.840 --> 00:37:19.560
Je peux te demander un truc ?

00:37:20.120 --> 00:37:21.080
Ce que tu veux.

00:37:23.440 --> 00:37:24.920
Tu te démerdes comme tu veux,

00:37:26.040 --> 00:37:27.720
mais tu fais sourire ma femme.

00:37:30.040 --> 00:37:31.760
Moi, je vais plus pouvoir.

00:37:36.320 --> 00:37:37.520
Promis.

00:37:39.240 --> 00:37:40.120
OK.

00:37:42.800 --> 00:37:44.160
Merci pour le bouquin.

00:37:44.800 --> 00:37:47.920
J'ai ce que je voulais.
Faut que je venge mon père, maintenant.

00:38:06.680 --> 00:38:08.880
J'ai été ravi de faire votre connaissance.

00:38:11.920 --> 00:38:13.360
Faut tenir le coup, Djibril.

00:38:17.200 --> 00:38:18.040
Merci.

00:38:39.480 --> 00:38:40.480
[détenu] Bonne nuit.

00:38:43.440 --> 00:38:46.440
[comptine "Alouette" sifflée]

00:39:03.120 --> 00:39:04.080
[Claire] Raoul.

00:39:04.160 --> 00:39:06.480
Tu poses ton livre et tu éteins,
s'il te plaît.

00:39:11.320 --> 00:39:12.560
Allez.

00:39:16.160 --> 00:39:17.160
Bonne nuit.

00:39:46.320 --> 00:39:47.960
Allez, go.

00:39:54.640 --> 00:39:58.320
Hé, si tu trouves un indice
dans Harry Potter, tu nous appelles.

00:39:59.800 --> 00:40:00.960
[il rit]

00:40:01.040 --> 00:40:03.280
- À demain.
- Tu me déposes, Christian ?

00:40:03.360 --> 00:40:04.840
- Avec plaisir, viens.
- Cool.

00:40:05.520 --> 00:40:07.160
À demain, Youssef.

00:40:36.240 --> 00:40:38.120
[elle crie] Non !

00:40:39.280 --> 00:40:42.720
À l'aide ! Surveillant !

00:40:42.800 --> 00:40:45.800
[alarme]

00:41:02.840 --> 00:41:04.080
C'est bon, c'est fait ?

00:41:05.000 --> 00:41:07.880
- Pas de problème ?
- Non, au contraire.

00:41:07.960 --> 00:41:09.320
C'était trop facile.

00:41:10.440 --> 00:41:12.480
Ce bâtard était pas dans sa cellule.

00:41:13.440 --> 00:41:15.080
Je sais pas comment il a fait.

00:41:16.440 --> 00:41:18.960
Je l'ai retrouvé de l'autre côté,
dans les douches.

00:41:19.840 --> 00:41:21.360
Il s'était pendu.

00:41:28.640 --> 00:41:31.760
[sirène d'ambulance]

00:41:36.720 --> 00:41:38.160
[musique suspense]

00:41:48.240 --> 00:41:51.680
[Raoul] "De tous les arts,
l'illusion est sans doute le plus subtil.

00:41:53.280 --> 00:41:55.160
Il nécessite toujours du doigté.

00:42:07.280 --> 00:42:09.720
Et parfois, une bonne dose de courage."

00:42:10.640 --> 00:42:14.080
[rythme cardiaque ralenti]

00:42:20.720 --> 00:42:23.480
[Assane] "Mais finalement,
peu importe la manière,

00:42:23.560 --> 00:42:25.280
car seul compte le résultat."

00:42:26.280 --> 00:42:29.840
[rythme cardiaque ralenti]

00:42:29.920 --> 00:42:31.600
[sirène d'ambulance]

00:42:32.120 --> 00:42:34.960
- Vu son état, pas la peine.
- Ouais.

00:42:35.040 --> 00:42:38.480
[Raoul] "Et évidemment,
le plaisir d'avoir trompé son monde."

00:42:39.400 --> 00:42:41.000
[musique suspense]

00:43:28.680 --> 00:43:29.880
Bonjour, monsieur.

00:43:36.680 --> 00:43:37.680
Pardon.

00:43:37.760 --> 00:43:38.840
Excusez-moi.

00:43:57.920 --> 00:43:58.960
Assane…

00:44:00.120 --> 00:44:01.440
Assane !

00:44:01.520 --> 00:44:03.920
Il y a 25 ans, vous avez piégé mon père.

00:44:07.440 --> 00:44:09.160
Qu'est-ce que vous lui avez fait ?

00:44:10.720 --> 00:44:11.840
Assane…

00:44:12.640 --> 00:44:14.360
Qu'est-ce que vous lui avez fait ?

00:44:21.200 --> 00:44:22.840
Je lui ai fait signer ses aveux.

00:44:27.800 --> 00:44:30.560
- Mais je suis innocent !
- C'est pas la question.

00:44:30.640 --> 00:44:32.640
- Si !
- Faites-moi confiance.

00:44:32.720 --> 00:44:35.800
Il vaut mieux être coupable et libre
qu'innocent et en prison.

00:44:36.440 --> 00:44:39.120
Alors, signez. Pensez à votre fils.

00:44:41.840 --> 00:44:43.040
Pour Assane.

00:44:48.600 --> 00:44:51.520
[Anne] Ses aveux devaient lui garantir
une remise de peine.

00:44:53.120 --> 00:44:56.640
On m'avait dit que le juge serait sensible
à votre situation familiale.

00:44:57.840 --> 00:45:00.600
Un immigré sénégalais
qui élève seul son fils en France.

00:45:01.760 --> 00:45:03.680
Mais le juge a été tellement sévère…

00:45:05.680 --> 00:45:08.320
Ton père ne l'a pas supporté.
Il s'est pendu.

00:45:09.560 --> 00:45:11.960
Les aveux qui devaient le sauver
l'ont condamné.

00:45:12.440 --> 00:45:13.720
J'ai été naïve.

00:45:15.800 --> 00:45:17.520
Il y avait des arrangements…

00:45:17.600 --> 00:45:22.040
Ça, c'est bon pour les gens comme vous.
Jamais pour les gens comme mon père.

00:45:23.120 --> 00:45:25.280
Après sa mort, je t'ai aidé, Assane.

00:45:25.360 --> 00:45:26.640
Je t'ai aidé.

00:45:27.440 --> 00:45:28.800
Je l'ai fait de loin.

00:45:30.520 --> 00:45:32.000
De loin, mais je t'ai aidé.

00:45:34.760 --> 00:45:35.600
C'était vous ?

00:45:38.320 --> 00:45:41.520
Ce généreux donateur… C'était vous ?

00:45:46.400 --> 00:45:49.000
Je me sentais responsable
de ta situation.

00:45:49.920 --> 00:45:52.440
Je voulais acheter ton pardon
et celui de ton père.

00:45:53.800 --> 00:45:56.320
- Je pensais à ton père…
- Ce brave Babakar !

00:45:56.400 --> 00:46:00.680
On l'accuse, on le pousse au suicide
et on se donne bonne conscience.

00:46:00.760 --> 00:46:02.560
Je l'ai accusé de rien !

00:46:03.880 --> 00:46:06.320
Un policier m'avait juré
qu'il allait l'aider !

00:46:06.400 --> 00:46:09.080
- C'est ça, l'histoire. Il a menti.
- Quel policier ?

00:46:11.040 --> 00:46:12.600
Quel policier ?

00:46:12.680 --> 00:46:16.240
- C'est trop loin, tout ça…
- [en hurlant] Non ! Quel policier ?

00:46:18.120 --> 00:46:19.040
Son nom.

00:46:24.880 --> 00:46:27.240
- [Anne] Dumont. Il s'appelait Dumont.
- Noyau.

00:46:27.320 --> 00:46:28.800
Inspecteur Dumont.

00:46:32.160 --> 00:46:35.520
Il savait que mon père avait confiance
en vous et il s'en est servi.

00:46:37.560 --> 00:46:39.680
- Pourquoi il a fait ça ?
- J'en sais rien.

00:46:40.520 --> 00:46:42.640
J'ai longtemps cherché
mais j'en sais rien.

00:46:44.560 --> 00:46:45.800
Assane.

00:46:47.080 --> 00:46:47.960
Je le jure.

00:46:54.560 --> 00:46:57.760
[brouhaha de cour d'école]

00:47:05.720 --> 00:47:08.760
- Où est-ce que tu vas comme ça, toi ?
- Il s'est perdu.

00:47:08.840 --> 00:47:11.920
Il est pas mal, son déguisement !
Tourne-toi, pour voir.

00:47:12.000 --> 00:47:14.480
Il s'est trompé,
il cherche la sortie de service.

00:47:14.560 --> 00:47:18.560
Restons polis, c'est pas comme ça
qu'on traite les nouveaux.

00:47:21.080 --> 00:47:24.040
Excuse-les, ils sont nés
avec de la merde dans la tête.

00:47:25.280 --> 00:47:26.200
Benjamin Ferel.

00:47:27.400 --> 00:47:29.400
- Assane Diop.
- Enchanté, Assane.

00:47:36.520 --> 00:47:39.400
[quelqu'un monte les marches]

00:47:43.840 --> 00:47:45.240
[soupir de soulagement]

00:48:06.040 --> 00:48:08.040
[musique douce]

00:48:10.560 --> 00:48:12.760
[dialogue inaudible à la télé]

00:48:35.480 --> 00:48:36.640
[la porte se referme]

00:49:06.680 --> 00:49:08.560
[Comet] Je peux te demander un truc ?

00:49:10.040 --> 00:49:11.800
Tu te démerdes comme tu veux,

00:49:12.680 --> 00:49:14.680
mais tu fais sourire ma femme.

00:49:16.360 --> 00:49:17.760
[musique suspense]